@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@userId = 1

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Portfolio - valor total, cash disponible y posiciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/portfolio/{{userId}}

### Buscar activos por ticker o nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/instruments/search?q=GGAL

### Buscar activos por nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/instruments/search?q=Galicia

### Listar órdenes del usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/user/{{userId}}

### Orden MARKET de compra por monto en pesos
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "instrumentId": 2,
  "side": "BUY",
  "type": "MARKET",
  "amount": 50000
}

### Orden MARKET de compra por cantidad de acciones
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "instrumentId": 2,
  "side": "BUY",
  "type": "MARKET",
  "quantity": 10
}

### Orden LIMIT de compra
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "instrumentId": 2,
  "side": "BUY",
  "type": "LIMIT",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 800
}

### Orden MARKET de venta
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "instrumentId": 2,
  "side": "SELL",
  "type": "MARKET",
  "quantity": 3
}

### Cancelar orden LIMIT (solo estado NEW)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1
}
